### Lấy tất cả review
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

### Lấy review theo ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

### Tạo review mới
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reviewerId": "64f7a1b2c9e77b001f8e2e1f",       
  "targetType": "room",                             
  "targetId": "64f7b3d7c9e77b001f8e2e20",         
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Phòng sạch sẽ, dịch vụ ok!",
  "status": "active"
}

### Cập nhật review
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 4,
  "comment": "Phòng đẹp nhưng hơi ồn",
  "status": "active"
}

### Xoá review
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reviews
Content-Type: application/json
